             was indicted for <rs id="t18180401-116-off645" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18180401-116-off645" type="offenceCategory" value="deception"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18180401-116-off645" type="offenceSubcategory" value="fraud"></interp>
               obtaining, by false pretences, 3l. in monies numbered
            </rs>, the monies of the 
               <persName id="t18180401-116-victim856" type="victimName">inhabitants of St. Giles's Without, Cripplegate<interp inst="t18180401-116-victim856" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
